Support
Path of the Wizard;;1;Your Hero gains an extra 5 Mana and 0.1 Mana Regen for every level gained.
Arcane Precision;;1;Inner area damage increased by 33%.
Shield Dust;;1;Increase number of Basic Attack blocks to 3.
Bribe;;1;Kill enemy Minions to gain stacks of Bribe. Use 20 stacks to bribe target Mercenary, instantly defeating them. Does not work on Golem.
Anti-magic Powder;;4;Block one instance of Spell damage by 50%.
Protective Shield;;4;Activate to shield an allied Hero from 330-1200 (300 + 30 per level) damage for 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Envenom;;4;Activate to poison an enemy hero, dealing 210-1080 (180 + 30 per level) damage over 6 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Promote;;4;Activate to give target allied lane Minion +200% permanent Health and +100% permanent damage. Has 2 charges. 60s cooldown.
Gust of Healing (Trait);;7;Activate to release a Soothing Mist every second for 4 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Regenerative Rains (Trait);;7;Soothing Mist activates each time you use an Ability.
Calldown: MULE;;7;Activate to calldown a Mule that repairs Structures, one at a time, near target point for 60 seconds, healing for 100 Health every 1 second. Grants 1 ammo every 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Cleanse;;7;Removes all stuns, roots, silences, and slows from the target and prevents their reapplication for 1 second. 30s cooldown.
Emerald Wind;;10;Creates an expanding nova of energy, dealing 130-1000 (100 + 30 per level) damage and pushing enemies away. 60s cooldown.
Blink Heal;;10;Teleport to nearby ally, healing them for 115-550 (100 + 15 per level). 2 charges. 8s charge cooldown. 1s cooldown.
Sticky Flare;;13;Targets are slowed by 30% Movement Speed for 3 seconds.
Phase Shield;;13;After finishing the teleport, the target of your Phase Shift gains a 225-950 (200 + 25 per level) point shield for 3 seconds.
Sprint;;13;Activate to gain 75% Movement Speed for 3 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Ice Block;;13;Activate to place yourself in stasis and gain invulnerability for 3 seconds. 80s cooldown.
Sticky Powder;;16;Polymorph targets are slowed by 50% Movement Speed.
Critterize;;16;Polymorphed targets take 25% more damage.
Rewind;;16;Activate to reduce the cooldown of your Basic Abilities by 10 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Stoneskin;;16;Activate to gain 30% of your max Health as Shields for 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Bolt of the Storm;;20;Activate to teleport to a nearby location. 40s cooldown.
Storm Shield;;20;Activate to give all nearby allied Heroes a Shield for 20% of their max Health for 3 seconds. 45s cooldown.
Continuous Winds;;20;Releases two additional novas that deal 25% damage.
Ysera's Blessing;;20;Increase maximum charges to 3.